    "1. Go to https://console.firebase.google.com",
    "2. Create (or select) a project",
    "3. Click 'Add app' → Android",
    "4. Enter package name: com.healthmonitor",
    "5. Download the real google-services.json",
    "6. Replace this entire file with the downloaded file",
    "7. In Firebase Console: enable Email/Password auth",
    "8. In Firebase Console: create a Firestore database (start in test mode)",
    "9. In Firebase Console: enable Cloud Messaging"
